@startuml
!include _style.puml
title AS-IS 05 — UML 시퀀스: 정상 자동/수동 저장

actor User
participant "App / Atlas / Bridge" as Editor
participant "기존 로컬 save" as Base
participant "Normalized Sync" as Sync
participant "v17 frame flush" as Flush
database "localStorage" as LS
participant "Supabase RPC" as RPC
database "PostgreSQL" as DB
participant "상단 상태 UI" as UI

User -> Editor : 데이터 편집
Editor -> Base : save()
Base -> LS : 해당 모듈 로컬 저장
Base --> Editor : 저장 완료
Base -> Sync : wrapper markChanged(reason)
Sync -> LS : meta dirty=true\ngeneration++
Sync -> UI : local=saved, server=queued

alt 자동 저장
  Sync -> Sync : debounce 550~800ms
else 수동 "지금 저장" / Ctrl+S
  User -> Sync : flushNow(manual)
end

Sync -> UI : local/server=saving
Sync -> Flush : v17FlushAllStores()
Flush -> Editor : iframe export request
Editor --> Flush : first valid Atlas/Bridge snapshot
Flush -> LS : App·Atlas·Bridge 저장
Flush --> Sync : unified payload
Sync -> Sync : validate(payload)
Sync -> Sync : stable hash
Sync -> Sync : operationId=uuid()
Sync -> RPC : ipe_commit_state(\nexpectedRevision, operationId, hash, payload)
RPC -> DB : workspace row lock
RPC -> DB : validate + projection replace
RPC -> DB : append revision
DB --> RPC : revision
RPC --> Sync : revision, replayed
Sync -> RPC : ipe_load_head()
RPC -> DB : load latest revision JSON
DB --> RPC : revision + payloadHash
RPC --> Sync : head
Sync -> LS : serverRevision/hash/dirty=false
Sync -> UI : local=saved, server=saved

note over Sync
  [S] 정상 경로에는 collect → validate → hash →
  optimistic commit → head verify가 존재한다.
end note

note right of Sync
  [S] operationId는 commitOnce 안에서 생성되어
  이 호출의 메모리 수명에만 존재한다.
end note

caption 정상 경로는 일관되지만 입력 snapshot의 권위와 실패 후 operation 수명은 보장하지 않는다.
@enduml
